data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 3-bedroom residence in Shadowlake offers a bonus enclosed study that can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom. Enjoy privacy on a cul-de-sac lot with no rear neighbors and a spacious backyard oasis perfect for relaxation. Inside, discover elegant touches like wood and tile flooring, tray ceilings, crown molding, and a charming formal dining area. With style, comfort, and functionality, this home is ready for you to make it yours!
